Class UserBaseUIElement

java.lang.Object
  cloudsim.ext.gui.SimulationUIElement
      cloudsim.ext.gui.UserBaseUIElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class UserBaseUIElement
extends SimulationUIElement
implements java.io.Serializable

UserBaseUIElement encapsulates the User Base specific data for the use of GUI classes. This information is used by Simulation to construct UserBases when initialising the simulation.
